## `EmbeddingProvider` trait

Central abstraction for all AI embedding work. Lives in
`crates/u-forge-core/src/ai/embeddings.rs`. **All new embedding providers must
implement this trait. Do not call HTTP clients or model APIs directly from
business logic.**

Why: the queue, search, and ingest pipelines consume the trait object. Bypassing
it means each call site re-invents batching, error handling, and dimension
checks. `LemonadeProvider` (`lemonade/embedding.rs`) is the only current impl;
FastEmbed and ONNX were removed.

`model_info()` returns our own `EmbeddingModelInfo` — **not** fastembed's
`ModelInfo`. The two were easy to confuse when fastembed was still in-tree.

`EmbeddingProviderType` has a single variant: `Lemonade`. The speculative
`Ollama` and `Cloud` variants were removed — do not re-add them without a
concrete provider landing alongside them.

---

## `TranscriptionProvider` trait

Same shape as `EmbeddingProvider`. Two concrete impls with a deliberate design
split:

- `LemonadeTranscriptionProvider` — simple, no GPU lock. Use for NPU FLM whisper
  and standalone cases.
- `LemonadeSttProvider` — shares `Arc<GpuResourceManager>` with the LLM chat
  provider. Use whenever STT may contend with LLM on the same GPU.

Construct directly — there is no `TranscriptionManager`. To wire into the queue,
go through `ProviderFactory::build` with `Capability::Transcription`.

---

## `KnowledgeGraph` invariants

- `::new(db_path: &Path)` is **synchronous** and takes **one argument**. Creates
  `<db_path>/knowledge.db` automatically. No async, no server needed.
- Holds `Arc<KnowledgeGraphStorage>` and `Arc<SchemaManager>` — no embedding
  field, no `InferenceQueue`, no Lemonade dependency.

Why: storage and schema operations must work in tests and in the UI with zero
external services. AI is opt-in at the caller. Do not regress this by adding an
embedding field to `KnowledgeGraph`.

Removed in earlier refactors — **these do not exist, do not reference them:**
`embedding_manager` field, `get_embedding_provider()` method,
`embedding_cache_dir` constructor arg, `FastEmbedProvider`,
`try_new_local_default`, `FASTEMBED_CACHE_PATH`, `EmbeddingManager`,
`TranscriptionManager`, the `DeviceWorker` trait, the `hardware/` module.

