## Testing

All tests use `TempDir` for isolation. See
[testing-debugging.mdc](mdc:.rulesdir/testing-debugging.mdc) for the mock
provider impls (`MockEmbeddingProvider`, `MockTranscriptionProvider`), the
`make_silence_wav` audio helper, and the `require_integration_url!()` skip
guard.

**Never share a `KnowledgeGraph` between tests** — always construct a fresh one
in a fresh `TempDir`. The `_tmp` binding must outlive the graph (TempDir deletes
on drop).

