## Agent Tool Arg Validation

Tool args in `u-forge-agent` are validated against JSON Schema before deserialization. Do not call `serde_json::from_value` directly on a raw tool arg payload — call `tool_validation::validate_tool_args(tool_name, &raw)?` first. The validated value is then safe to deserialize into the typed Args struct.
